Location: Republic of Nauru, Micronesia. \nUS Special Forces have been dispatched aboard the USS Humphreys to a small island recently occupied by North Korean Forces. Multiple Alien crash sites have been detected in proximity to the McTiller Martins facility and should be secured as quickly as possible.

Location: Kiribati, Oceania. \nFollowing the alien crisis, the small island of Kiribati became a focal point for multiple alien incursions. The Prototype Factory located there is the world leader for alien studies and has recently come under North Korean domination. US Special Forces have been sent via submarine to retake the facility and the surrounding peninsula.

Location: Seonbong, North Korea. \nThis North Korean facility has been designated a focal point for liberation by United States forces. A nano-suit equipped team has been ordered to secure the facilities there, including a previously unknown Prototype Installation.

Location: near Blackhawk, Colorado. \nIn a daring move, North Korean Special Forces have infiltrated a McTiller Martins Prototype facility in an attempt to retrieve alien technology. A nearby US Base has scrambled a nano-equipped team to engage and expel the forces from the area. Multiple automated factories are also located in the area and may be captured and used to supplement forces if needed.

Location: Caraga Region, Philippines. \nUS and North Korean Special Forces teams have been ordered to secure a small area in the Philippines that has multiple confirmed alien crash sites. A small research dome has been constructed in the area and may be used to process alien energy for use against hostile forces.

Location: Jaluit Atoll. \nA lethal standoff of North Korean and US Special Forces has occurred on a military airstrip located in the Marshall Islands. Both sides have been ordered to sweep and destroy the entire area of all enemy units. Fully functioning war factories and air factories make taking and holding this location critical to overall success.
Location: Molokai, Hawaii. \nAn abandoned steel mill has been taken and is now used as a training facility for nano-suit equipped troops. This facility is perfect for simulating urban combat.

Location: Moorea, French Polynesia. \nAn old military railway terminal has been converted into a multi-zone training facility. Rooftops are critical to maintaining dominance over the immediate combat area. Multiple advanced weapons have been hidden around the engagement area to facilitate field response to rapidly changing conditions.

Location: Guam. \nA hidden outpost in a remote location has been chosen for testing alien weapons and materials. Special Forces assigned to protect this crucial scientific area have been using one of the less frequented zones for weapons and tactics training.

Location: Ebeye, Marshall Islands. \nAn old gypsum mine has been turned into a training ground for advanced special ops combat. In preparation for an upcoming assault on North Korean territory, you have been selected to train in this location.

Location: Southern Pacific Ocean. \nThe USS Humphreys has been temporarily converted into a covert training area. Many of the ship’s areas are locked down and off limits but most of it has been made available for advanced weapon testing and combat simulation.
Location: Marine Corp Base Hawaii. \nAn advanced vehicle training course has been constructed in an extinct volcano and is now available for all motorized testing and tactics practice.

Location: Solomon islands. \nIn the search for possible underground Alien artifacts, the US government has started digging operations in different regions. This one has been abandoned after the conflict started.

Location: Bali, Indonesia. \nA minor earthquake destroyed the access routes to this prototype factory, making it difficult to exploit. However, the accrued greed for alien energy made this installation worth fighting for.

Location: Datai Bay, Langkawi. \nNext to an abandoned resort, isolated in the island's northern forest, a prototype factory has been built after the discovery of additional alien crash sites. The old, twisted road network had to be restored in order to bring the US forces onsite to organize defense
Location: Paia, Hawaii. \nUS forces have set up a training field on the Hawaiian islands for the newest recruits and seasoned veterans alike to work on their team strategies.
Location: near Kanoya, Japan. \nAn abandoned graveyard has been the theater of an alien crash. Forces in presence must fight to get access to alien technology.
Location: Somewhere in the South Pacific. \nBlack Ops Transport flight Black Rose got slightly redirected by a tornado... the struggle for survival has begun!

Location: Ulaangom, Mongolia. \nDue to a translation error in a North Korean message hinting at alien presence, US forces launched an operation on this isolated monastery which quickly became the theater of a fierce battle for honor only.
Location: near Yantai, China. \nThis fishermen village is being contested by the belligerant forces due to its strategical position in front of the North Korean peninsula
Location: Somewhere in Borneo. \nThe conflict has become to intense that all places need to be conquered, including old outposts used by local tribes to control a forest area
Welcome to Power Struggle, Basic Tutorial

As a Special Forces Operative, you have been selected to capture and secure priceless Alien Technology. To accomplish this you must eliminate the enemy presence in this region. This instructional video will help guide you to victory.

As a fresh recruit, you have only been cleared for limited weapons and equipment access. To earn advanced equipment, you must prove yourself in battle by earning Prestige. These points are earned by accomplishing objectives and neutralizing enemy units.
You can use your tactical map to view the entire battlefield and set your own objectives.

This is a Prototype Laboratory. Capturing this building will allow you to produce super high tech equipment and alien devices. These destructive weapons are needed to eliminate the enemy headquarters.

To capture this building, position yourself by the Core Terminal inside the Command Point. Here your nanosuit on board computer will automatically interface with the main terminal, and the progress of your capture will be displayed on your HUD.
Creating Alien technology requires a special energy source located at known alien crash sites. You must secure these areas by moving to these sites and controlling them.
By capturing and holding both the prototype factory and the alien crash sites, you will gain access to high tech artifacts that will allow you to destroy the enemy’s hardened headquarters.
These items are available at the Prototype factory as soon as high enough levels of alien energy have been reached.
These levels will be tracked in the upper center of your HUD. Holding the Prototype factory is critical to your team’s success, so do not lose it after capturing it.
Most maps also contain special strategic locations that will help you accomplish your goals.
The War Factory is capable of producing Armored Units like Tanks and ICVs.
The Air Factory enables you to produce Helicopters and VTOLs.
The Naval Factory allows production of boats and amphibious vessels.
Finally, strategic bunkers allow soldiers entering the battlefield to deploy at strategic locations. Capturing and holding these areas are critical to proper mobilization of your forces.
However, each HQ is protected by multiple automatic turrets that will track and destroy all hostile units.
In order to position you high yield weapon safely within range of the enemy HQ, you must first neutralize its turret defenses.
Victory and Glory are ultimately achieved when the enemy HQ is obliterated.
To defeat your enemy their HQ must be destroyed. This is achieved with High Yield weapons such as the Tac Launcher, ...
